OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine, but chilly start with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine. Clouding over from the
OL,7,Fnorthwest during the morning, with the
OL,8,Fodd spot of rain possible. Turning
OL,9,Fmuch sunnier again towards the end of
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Temperatures near
OL,11,Faverage, but a cooling breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening
OL,14,Fwith clear periods. Most places
OL,15,Fstaying frost free as cloud moves in
OL,16,Ffrom the north just before dawn,
OL,17,Fbringing some showers, and winds
OL,18,Ffreshen.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
