OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,6,Fscattered blustery showers, the
OL,7,Fshowers locally heavy with some strong
OL,8,Fgusts, mainly around coasts. Chilly,
OL,9,Fwith temperatures below average for
OL,10,Fthe time of year.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FStaying unsettled on Thursday with
OL,14,Fsome showery rain, and brisk winds.
OL,15,FDrier and brighter on Friday and
OL,16,FSaturday, with winds easing.
OL,17,FTemperatures staying below average for
OL,18,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
